{
  "stem": "24397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met and-- and had a normal kind of attraction boy meets girl have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at the same time, her background and my background, I think in addition to having-- wanting to live in Israel as well, we had so many things in common that gave us a real kind of common interest that was beyond just the fascination of-- of physical attraction.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were seeing each other every trip I came here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was kind of a long-distance courtship for a year or more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we got married here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what made you decide to leave Israel?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was-- you see, I thought I'd planned everything perfectly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had planned what kind of a job to take to do at sea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I even took electronics and radio at sea so that I could move into the-- leave the ships and get a job ashore, which I did.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked for IBM there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing you can't plan is how healthy your kids are going to be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my son, older son who's autistic, we didn't know what-- actually what he had or what he was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We just knew there was a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had lots of different labels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said he was aphasic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we went and had therapy once a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then that therapy wasn't-- couldn't be paid for anymore by the medical plan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the person who was giving the therapy was trained in America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember she told us that, you know, if you go to the States, there are special schools for this kind of problem and they'd be there six hours a day, seven hours a day every day.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is what you should do for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
